=== Ansible Context Garden ===

A curated set of references, keywords, and descriptions designed to quickly bootstrap an Ansible playbook Paracel session.

--- CORE CONCEPTS ---
[Ansible Structure]
- playbooks: YAML files describing tasks and roles
- inventory: list of hosts/groups (INI or YAML)
- modules: built-in commands like copy, template, yum, apt, service, user

[Playbook Structure]
- ---
  - name: description
  - hosts: target
  - become: yes (sudo)
  - tasks: list of steps to execute

[Common Modules]
- file, stat, debug, copy, template, get_url
- package (yum/apt), service, user, group
- shell, command, raw (when necessary)

[Variables and Facts]
- vars:, vars_files:, set_fact
- {{ variable }}, hostvars, group_vars/all.yml

[Handlers & Roles]
- notify: handlers
- handlers: name: restart service
- roles/: tasks/, handlers/, templates/, defaults/

[Loops and Conditions]
- with_items, when, register, until, retries, delay

[Vault and Secrets]
- ansible-vault encrypt/decrypt/view/edit
- --ask-vault-pass

[Execution CLI]
- ansible-playbook site.yml -i inventory.ini
- ansible all -m ping -i hosts
- --check, --diff, --limit, --tags

[Resources]
- https://docs.ansible.com/
- https://galaxy.ansible.com/
- https://github.com/geerlingguy/ansible-for-devops
